<%= render 'shared/content_title', title: 'Log in' %>

You account is locked. You will receive a text message with a pin number. Enter the pin number to unlock your account and proceed with login.
<div class='well'>
  <%= form_tag '/pin' do %>
    <div class='control-group'>
      <%= label_tag :pin, 'Pin Number' %>
      <%= text_field_tag :pin %>
    </div>
     <%= submit_tag 'Unlock your account', class:'btn btn-success' %>
  <% end %>
</div>